{"tid":353331,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(方丈）一人一個小器既朋友和事","createTime":"2017-08-09T13:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T15:49:46.000Z","uid":37203,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a88c2a1b0b755ccff92feeead8ce500ef575035e","tid":353331,"uid":37203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:28:40.000Z","msg":"講講背景先，話説我就識得一個成日慨嘆自己懷材不遇，一有人讚佢就即刻擺上fb ig既攝影朋友，之前就做過coffee shop, 俾人炒又話自己走係公司損失，成日呢就叫大家like佢d攝影page, 但一唔係影得靚，二成日自拍自己個撚樣叫春。三就間唔時開post話刪咗d人，你仲見到我即係我當你朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當自己好撚重要咁，我有一次俾佢invite我like佢d相啦，我唔理佢，即刻用佢所有ac unfollow我又剩咁。各位巴打又有無遇過呢d小器朋友<br />\n<br />\nSorry 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1767118bd684fe4a81421076fdc5cf737c0b9cd","tid":353331,"uid":37203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:38:47.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"468dc621270a8547ed3bcd541383bfbd29042aba","tid":353331,"uid":37203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:42:43.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"77062bbe8c957031857a7c3d63f9c4382eaed98c","tid":353331,"uid":21480,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e08e8b11e80510470c3f6faaa62ee702b2675d0e","tid":353331,"uid":37203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次借左朋友五十蚊 成年都冇還 仲周圍唱我唔還錢<br />\n鬼咁小器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n借到係我既本事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你50都唔肯還。又真係仆街咗少少既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9636477eb09765db12a0f6d004f8ffaa24ab8a62","tid":353331,"uid":37203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:14:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a3c654f793e7cb86f19d98251542fadec9385f1","tid":353331,"uid":37203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:18:18.000Z","msg":"推，